      },
      "date": "2012-12-28 09:53:06.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 8: (1 inline comment)\n\nI don't understand one moment: ofd_fid_set_index() is called from connect() and sets ofd->ofd_seq_site.ss_node_id()\n\nshould this index be set once from OSTXXXX name?",
