        "username": "bzzz"
      },
      "date": "2012-12-29 05:56:56.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 8:\n\nsorry, it's still not clear to me.. in OST_CONNECT MDS reports own index, so that number of MDS could have own groups (before). IOW, those indices are different and they are different from OST index? but in FLDB we want OST index, right?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "fd8dfd3fd3388aff5dbb3887f6c1ffea706ae33d",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 12,
