        "email": "di.wang@intel.com",
        "username": "wangdi",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2012-12-29 06:26:32.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 8:\n\nSorry, I am a little confused about your question. It is my understanding that the index got from CONNECTION req(OST_CONNECT_MDS) should be the same as the index we got from obd_name, right?   yes, the index is needed for allocating the seq.",
