      },
      "date": "2012-12-29 06:34:58.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 8:\n\nno, i was wrong - confused that index with group we used to set with set_info(MDS_CONN). though still OST index is supposed to be set and working with no connection from MDS. IOW, it's better to be taken from OST name.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 8
    },
